<section id="about" class="feature">
    <div class="row" data-bottom="transform:translateY(-5em)" data--100-bottom="transform:translateY(0)">
        <div class="large-12 columns social">
            <% if @item[:tweet_link] %>
                <a rel="nofollow" href="<%= @item[:tweet_link] %>" target="_blank" title="Tweet hashtag #now" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'social', 'twitter')"><i class="icon-twitter-2"></i></a>
            <% end %>
            <% if @item[:facebook_link] %>
                <a rel="nofollow" href="<%= @item[:facebook_link] %>" target="_blank" title="Facebook page" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'social', 'facebook')"><i class="icon-facebook-2"></i></a>
            <% end %>
            <a rel="nofollow" href="mailto:now@thoughtworks.com" title="Email us" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'social', 'email')"><i class="icon-mail"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns" data-anchor-target="#_about">
            <h4>NETWORK OF WOMEN</h4>
            <p id="_about" data--100-bottom-top="transform:perspective(400px) rotateX(90deg) scale(.5);transform-origin:50% 0" data--100-bottom="transform:perspective(400px) rotateX(0deg) scale(1)">
            <br>ThoughtWorks N.O.W.  is a growing and connected community of women from all walks of life, looking to be a part of an open and inclusive network, to come together to learn from each other and be inspired. It provides a positive and motivating environment by bringing fresh content and wonderful speakers.
            <br>After successfully conducting the events in <a href="https://thoughtworks-bangalore.github.io/NOW/" class="link"><em>Bangalore</em></a> and <a href="https://www.meetup.com/ThoughtWorks-GeekNight-Pune/events/258983469/" class="link"><em>Pune</em></a>, for the first time, we are launching the event in Hyderabad. It is a one-day event to celebrate women leaders. Our goal is to facilitate an aspirational, relevant and engaging dialogue with leaders across domains and translate these experiences
            <br>We have an exciting day planned with keynote, sessions, panel discussion and a workshop. There is a stellar line up of speakers, each with a unique and inspiring story to share.
            <br>For any further questions / suggestions write to us at:
                <br> <a href="mailto:now@thoughtworks.com" class="link"><em>now@thoughtworks.com</em></a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
